snippet.title: EVE Frontier | Official Teaser Trailer | 'Awake Eternally'
snippet.description:
Developed by CCP Games, #EVEFrontier is a new space survival simulation defined by freedom, challenge and consequence. In the shadow of the Trinary who will you become?

Enter the Frontier, Awake Eternally.

Play Now: https://www.evefrontier.com/
Join Discord: https://www.discord.gg/evefrontier 

Follow us on:
https://twitter.com/EVE_Frontier
https://www.facebook.com/evefrontier
https://www.instagram.com/evefrontier
